title: Small business revenue change
caption: Daily change in small business revenue in Austin, TX identified as those having had at least 1 transaction in previous 3 days and categorized by industry sector. Entries between January 4th - January 31st of 2019 - present are used to determine relative change in entries for subsequent days of the respective year. Subsequently the change is seasonally adjusted where a year-over-year division is carried out between 2019 and other years and is presented as a 7-day moving average. The aforementioned preprocessing steps are performed by the data provider whom is referenced as the source.
